Affiliation = {Li, J (Corresponding Author), Guangzhou Univ, Coll Comp Sci \& Network Engn, Guangzhou, Peoples R China.
   Xing, Cipai; Chen, Zhuorong; Chen, Lexin; Li, Jin, Guangzhou Univ, Coll Comp Sci \& Network Engn, Guangzhou, Peoples R China.
