   Lin, Jun, Sun Yat Sen Univ, Guangzhou 510006, Guangdong, Peoples R China.
   Lin, Jun, China Elect Prod Reliabil \& Environm Testing Res I, Guangzhou 511370, Guangdong, Peoples R China.},
