   Chang, Hao, Jilin Normal Univ, Affiliated Expt Sch, Siping 136000, Peoples R China.
   Cheng, Feifei; Yang, Heming, Jilin Normal Univ, Sch Geog Sci \& Tourism, Siping 136000, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1038/s41598-024-57408-0},
