Affiliation = {Wang, Y (Corresponding Author), Macquarie Univ, Australian Inst Hlth Innovat, Ctr Hlth Informat, N Ryde, NSW, Australia.
   Wang, Ying; Coiera, Enrico; Magrabi, Farah, Macquarie Univ, Australian Inst Hlth Innovat, Ctr Hlth Informat, N Ryde, NSW, Australia.
