   Allaire, Douglas; Arroyave, Raymundo, Texas A\&M Univ, J Mike Dept Mech Engn Walker 66, College Stn, TX 77843 USA.
   Arroyave, Raymundo, Texas A\&M Univ, Wm Michael Barnes 64 Dept Ind \& Syst Engn, College Stn, TX USA.},
