   Sellami, Amira; Rekik, Mouna; Ben Njima, Chakib, Univ Sousse, Higher Inst Transport \& Logist Sousse, Sousse, Tunisia.
   Rekik, Mouna, Lab Multimedia, Informat Syst \& Adv Comp, Sfax, Tunisia.},
Keywords = {Extreme Gradient Boosting; Multitarget regression; Random Forest;
   Tribological performance; brake pad materials},
